overview.en: Since Satoshi Nakamoto proposed the Bitcoin genesis block in 2009, the total market value of the global cryptocurrency market has soared from 0 dollar to today's more than 100 billion dollars. 2014 witnessed the birth of Ethereum made a even crazy vision with smart contract. Jointly with the block-chain technology, it has created a dramatic growth of the global cryptocurrency market. What’s more, it was quietly developing the power that can transform the world.
overview.zh: 自2009年中本聪写下比特币创世区块以来，世界数字货币市场总市值从0 飙升至今天的数千亿美元。2014年以太坊诞生，又掀起了去中心化去信任应用（智能合约）席卷全球的狂潮，与区块链技术一同为全球数字货币市场增长创造了神话，更是在悄然酝酿着变革世界的力量。
